Package: customizableSteps
Title: Customizable Higher Order Recipes Step Functions
Version: 0.7.0.0
Authors@R: person("Lars", "Kjeldgaard", email = "lars.kjeldgaard@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Higher order step functions for the 'recipes' package. These 
    step functions take prep and bake helper functions as inputs and create 
    customized step functions as output.
